						               													<description>From the back of the box:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Blast! Card Game&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Blast is the colorful, fast moving dice and card game where you can really find out who your friends are.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player has to match the throw of the die with the cards in their hand in order to get most points and win the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game play is simple - just throw the dice and match the cards - a 'blue four' on the special color-coded dice together with a 'three' on the normal dice adds up to a 'BLUE SEVEN'. If you have the 'blue seven' card in your hand then you've scored seven points and it's your turn next with the dice.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;But watch out! You're never sure of the winner until the count is up. With careful use of your action cards you can blast your opponents, lower their score , and make yourself the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    36 Dice Cards&amp;#10;     19 Action Cards&amp;#10;     Special color Coded Dice&amp;#10;     Standard Dice&amp;#10;     Rules Inside&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Listed as ages 8 to adult.&amp;#10;My Waddingtons edition states it is under license from Family Games, Canada.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
